# VK Secondary Pages — Build Rules

## Section Rhythm (always follow this order)
1. **Hero** — `#EDE8E2` warm light, dark text, red eyebrow, red CTA button
2. **Strip / credential bar** — `var(--warm-white)`, thin border, no padding
3. **Grid / cards** — `var(--off-white)` bg, `#fff` cards, 1px rgba gap
4. **Content / body** — `#fff` bg, dark text
5. **CTA / form** — `#EDE8E2` bg, white inputs, red button
6. **Values bar** — `var(--off-white)` bg, `#fff` tiles, program-exclusive benefits only
7. **Footer** — standard template

## Color Rules
- `--vk-red: #C0392B` — all CTAs, eyebrows, accents on secondary pages
- `--near-black: #1A1A18` — all body text
- `--amber: #D4860A` — VINTAGE/USED content only. Never on new pages.
- `--amber-bg: #F5E6C8` — VINTAGE/USED only. Never on secondary program pages.
- `#EDE8E2` — hero and CTA section bg on all secondary pages
- BANNED: `rgba(192,57,43,0.04–0.08)` as standalone bg. Use `var(--off-white)`.
- BANNED: `#fde8e6`. Use `rgba(26,26,24,0.07)` for neutral pills.
- Form focus borders: always `var(--vk-red)` regardless of section bg.

## Typography
- Display/headings: Playfair Display — H1 48–56px, H2 32–40px, H3 18–22px
- Body: DM Sans — 13–17px
- Eyebrows: DM Sans, 12px, 0.18–0.22em letter-spacing, uppercase, `var(--vk-red)`
- Pricing: DM Sans only, font-weight 500, `var(--near-black)`. NEVER Playfair on numbers.
- Min font size: 12px everywhere.

## Build Speed Rules
- Pull hero copy, 3-step process, JSON-LD, and "what we buy" from `VK-secondary-pages-source.html` first
- Check live vintageking.com for the page — if 404, build from source + design system
- No ask-mode for pages with a spec in navigator.html
- Use existing build script pattern (`tools/build_*.py`)
- Always: light hero (`#EDE8E2`), never dark hero on secondary pages
- Always: white form inputs with dark text on light bg sections
- Always: update navigator.html (status, link, repo col, progress counter) after each page

## Values / Benefit Tiles
- Only show program-exclusive benefits (not things already in the nav bar)
- Never: "Free Shipping", "0% Financing" as tile headlines (already in topbar)
- Use: preferred pricing, account manager, trade credit, installs, warranty, priority service

## SEO / JSON-LD
- Every page needs at least one JSON-LD block (Service, HowTo, FAQPage, or JobPosting)
- Meta description: 140–160 chars, action-oriented
- Title: `[Page Name] — [Benefit Hook] | Vintage King`

## Navigator Updates (after every page)
- Status dot: `dot-done`
- Repo col: green `Yes — filename.html ↗`
- Page name col: plain text name + red `filename.html ↗` link below
- Sidebar blurb: update to reflect latest done page
- Progress counter: increment by 1, recalculate bar %

## Light Base — All Pages
- ALL pages start light. No dark heroes. Hero + CTA = `#EDE8E2`. Never a full dark/black first section.
- At most ONE dark accent block (`#2C2C2A`) per page, never first, optional quote/stat only.
- Gear heritage pages: large gear image in BODY first content section (min-height `520px`), not a dark hero.
- Section order: `#EDE8E2` hero → `var(--warm-white)` strip → `var(--off-white)` grid → `#fff` content → `#EDE8E2` CTA/form → `var(--off-white)` values bar → footer.

## No Physical Locations
- VK has NO showrooms, retail locations, or city offices.
- NEVER reference Detroit, Los Angeles, Nashville, or any city as a VK physical location.
- NEVER use "showroom", "visit us", "in-store", "demo room" language.
- Do NOT build location pages. `los-angeles.html` is cancelled.

## Image Placeholder Sizes
- Service pages — feature cards: min-height `280px`; portraits: min-height `260px` aspect-ratio `3/4`.
- Gear heritage pages — body gear image: `520px`; version cards: `320px`; timeline cards: `360px`; shop CTA: `300px`.
- All placeholders: `background:var(--off-white); border:1px solid rgba(26,26,24,0.08)`.

## Accent Toggle (Red / Amber)
- Every new page gets a small 2-button dev toggle: `A — Red` / `B — Amber` switching `--page-accent`.
- Red default: Careers, Studio Professionals, Trade Program, Audio Consultants, About VK.
- Amber default: PLAYBACK, Make Your Mark, Hall of Fame, all HOF gear pages, 25 Years.

## Mandatory Session Rules
- Never revert or overwrite completed work.
- Never revisit or fix anything already completed.
- No drift from current task. Precision edits only.

## GEO / AI Agent Signals
- Every page: one JSON-LD block (Service, HowTo, Article, JobPosting, or Product per type).
- Meta description 140–160 chars, action-oriented. Title: `[Name] — [Hook] | Vintage King`.
- Speakable class on hero `<p>` for Google SGE.
